docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout 1 2 3 4 mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. 情報の整理 やりたいこと → 調査 → 実践 → 失敗 → 調査... 繰り返してみる 過程を文書化し共有化 情報の発信 Ctrl Note test test test Tip test test test 定義語 例
